	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-477" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-147659" number="39596" version="2770">
			<HEADING>Chapter 22: Compost Facility Usage Rates</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19234" name="T16C022"/>Chapter 22: Compost Facility Usage Rates</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-147671" number="39597" version="2770">
								<HEADING>§ 22-01 Definitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19236" name="T16C022_22-01"/>§ 22-01 Definitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-147670" number="39598" version="2770">
									<PARA>For purposes of this chapter, the following terms have the following meanings: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-101]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-147669" number="39599" version="2770">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Compost Facility.</CHARFORMAT> “Compost facility” has the same meaning as in § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="16-129.1" destination-id="0-0-0-0">16-129.1</LINK> of the New York City Administrative Code. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-101]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-147668" number="39600" version="2770">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">CPI.</CHARFORMAT> “CPI” means the Consumer Price Index for all urban consumers, as defined by the United States Bureau of Labor Statistics, for the twelve months ended on June 30th. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-101]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-147667" number="39601" version="2771">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Department.</CHARFORMAT> “Department” means the Department of Sanitation. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-101]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-147666" number="39602" version="2770">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Organic Waste.</CHARFORMAT> “Organic waste” has the same meaning as in § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="16-303" destination-id="0-0-0-0">16-303</LINK> of the New York City Administrative Code, except for plant trimmings which may be considered yard waste if they contain no other organic wastes. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-101]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-147665" number="39603" version="2770">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Yard Waste.</CHARFORMAT> “Yard waste” has the same meaning as in § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="16-303" destination-id="0-0-0-0">16-303</LINK> of the New York City Administrative Code. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-101]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-147672" number="39604" version="2770">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 9/13/2024, eff. 10/13/2024) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-101]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-147664" number="39605" version="2770">
								<HEADING>§ 22-02 Rates of Charge.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19238" name="T16C022_22-02"/>§ 22-02 Rates of Charge.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-147663" number="39606" version="2770">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>a.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Pursuant to § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="16-129.1" destination-id="0-0-0-0">16-129.1</LINK> of the Administrative Code, the following rates will be charged and collected by the Commissioner from any person or entity depositing organic waste and/or yard waste at Department compost facilities: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-101]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-147662" number="39607" version="2770">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>1.<TAB tab-count="1"/>The rate for the disposal for leaf and yard waste will be $12 per cubic yard beginning October 15, 2024, and will be adjusted annually after July 1 thereafter in accordance with any change in the CPI. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-101]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-147661" number="39608" version="2770">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>2.<TAB tab-count="1"/>The rate for the disposal for organic waste will be $85 per ton beginning October 15, 2024, and will be adjusted annually after July 1 thereafter in accordance with any change in the CPI. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-101]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-147660" number="39609" version="2770">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>b.<TAB tab-count="1"/>The Department will publish the new rates, if any, in the City Record and on the Department’s website on or about August 1 every year with such rates becoming effective as of September 1 of such calendar year. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-101]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-147658" number="39610" version="2770">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 9/13/2024, eff. 10/13/2024) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-101]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
</DOCUMENT>